{"tid":360532,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要好好珍惜一個肯請你食飯嘅女朋友","createTime":"2017-08-15T11:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T15:36:05.000Z","uid":58575,"like":62,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30d13e006a3cef7bf3cfc4b6d9643f395c580461","tid":360532,"uid":58575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:04:21.000Z","msg":"行街食飯睇戲肯AA制嘅女朋友已經好唔話得 有時仲會肯請埋你食飯嘅女朋友邊到搵<br />\n<br />\n大家同年 一齊畢左業又未搵到工 大家都唔會問屋企拎錢嗰類人 只係用緊番pt儲落嘅少少錢 <br />\n<br />\n話說佢知道左我儲落嘅錢差唔多用得七七八八 於是近排食飯嗰陣佢都主動去比錢先 淨係同我講句話之後等你有錢先再請番我啦<br />\n<br />\n每一次睇住佢去比錢 自己想阻止但又有心無力嗰種無奈感 真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女朋友我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3611f4be922d3e8a7a0d37f166b06358ef068e0","tid":360532,"uid":828,"like":20,"dislike":14,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:07:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">通常都係因為做左d野對你唔住先會請你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee985dc8242e7ae3c1014df4a3af9194e17a0fa6","tid":360532,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">通常都係因為做左d野對你唔住先會請你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來係咁<br />\n錯d讚隻臭雞做乜咁好"},{"pid":"679978ab234e9ef8b12134ebd2a943595fce13f1","tid":360532,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"成日靜靜雞塞d錢畀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05404b82706165ba8ea369d18bd5336838f67815","tid":360532,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: green;\">通常都係因為做左d野對你唔住先會請你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n負評上一頁"},{"pid":"18fe8dab8d605ec3abc9f1a363ab10b40b309817","tid":360532,"uid":5857